  "riddle": "1. Begin your journey by investigating the legacy of a founder dedicated to communal harmony, who established an organization intertwined with Buddhist heritage.\n\n2. A temple steeped in tranquility awaits your visit; how many years ago was its sacred consecration commanded by faith?\n\n3. Travel next to where pilgrims walk a grand circuit — the distance stretches far, reaching numbers that can be converted into feet. What do you find in that transformation?\n\n4. Within a revered parikrama circuit lies a revered metric — how many kos encompass the entirety of this spiritual path?\n\n5. Venture southward to the ancient land renowned for its epic tales and battles. What is the elevation above sea level of this hallowed ground?\n\n6. In a bustling center of a rich city, squares connect stories; how many public squares burst forth in this vibrant locale, including the one that carries George's name?\n\n7. Turning to a serene resting place within the city's heart, seek the year when this sanctuary first opened its gates to honor the departed.\n\n8. Determine the day of the week that marked the dawn of the year mentioned in clue 7 — does it greet the week on a Monday or perhaps a Sunday?\n\n9. An urban landscape also cradles memory — discover the year when a cemetery was founded to commemorate lives lost in the nation's capital.\n\n10. In numerical form, unveil how many 1-bits light up when your previous discovery is cast in binary shadows.\n\n11. Find yourself in a vibrant district bustling with culture. How many languages intertwine in the narratives of this iconic area?\n\n12. Examine the elevation that cradles this spirited neighborhood; how high does it rise from the surrounding earth?\n\n13. As you continue to explore, seek out the number of sports stadiums that lie just around the corner from this lively neighborhood. \n\n14. Now combine the height of this district with the sporting excitement nearby: what remains when you take the absolute difference derived from both clues?\n\n15. Reflecting on the eclectic sights from clue 11, how many factors does that number possess? \n\n16. Seek the starting point of a landmark with rich history — which year marked the commencement of its construction?\n\n17. Complete your journey by calculating the digital root of the sacred numbers unearthed in clues 2 and 3; what does the culmination reveal as a single digit? \n\nThe final answer should yield a single digit (0-9) derived from your arithmetic journey.",
